Lloyd Blankfein - Wikipedia






















 






Lloyd Blankfein

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Lloyd C. Blankfein)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Lloyd Blankfein





Born
(1954-09-15) September 15, 1954 (age 62)
New York City, New York, U.S.


Nationality
American


Alma mater
Harvard University


Occupation
Chairman and CEO, Goldman Sachs


Years active
1982 - present


