 Goldman Sachs Chairman and CEO Lloyd C. Blankfein addresses uncertainty in the markets – stemming from policy changes, interest rate divergence and cyclical factors, among other developments – and whether the market environment warrants a more optimistic outlook for 2017.















 

Lloyd C. Blankfein
Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, Goldman Sachs
Read Bio
 




The change in the market today is from a cycle where we were of very low economic activity… and it feels like we’re changing into one which is going to get “growthier.” 
 - Lloyd C. Blankfein 







